data.description: Welcome to your charming oasis! This home is the perfect blend of convenience and peace. Located close to town, you can quickly get where you need to go without having to sacrifice your privacy. You'll also find a great elementary school nearby for all of your educational needs.   This home features a large backyard, giving you plenty of space for activities or just relaxing with guests. Plus, there's even an unfinished basement that offers endless possibilities for what you can make out of it - whether it be a den, workshop, or something else entirely! The carport provides added protection from the elements when coming and going from the house.   Don't miss this opportunity - come see this charming home today!
